                      <summary>A collection of letters addressed to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2853Borgia">Stefano
               Borgia</persName>, secretary of the Congregation de Propaganda Fide.</summary>
                    </msContents>

                    <physDesc>
