                            <locus from="352r" to="353r" facs="0359">Fols 352r–353r</locus>
                            <note>A letter in Italian from <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9535tobiyaG"> Ṭobiya Giyorgis Gäbrä Ǝgziʾabǝḥer </persName> to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2853Borgia">Stefano
               Borgia</persName>, dated <date>19 December 1788</date>, describing the provenance and contents of <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVborget24">Vat. Borg. et. 24</ref>, a scroll containing <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1758Lefafa#a1">Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq</ref>.</note>
